Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:35.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:39.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's weird... Where did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:41.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you looking for, little one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:46.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you see... I promised\Nto lend Kei-chan a book,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:49.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I seem to have lost\Nit somewhere around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:51.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... that sounds pretty troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:53.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:57.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was wondering where it was,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:02:59.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but you had it all this time, Lion-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:01.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:04.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That girl from last week was reading this book.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:06.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kei-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:09.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not her... the other person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean Marika-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:13.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah... her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:15.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:18.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Marika-chan was reading this back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:20.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:21.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:22.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is she doing all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:29.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So Lion-san only looks skin-deep!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:32.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess since Marika-chan is so pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:34.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's nothing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:36.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just... a bit concerned, that's all...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:37.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:39.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's just leave it as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:41.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, you've got it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:47.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? You'll be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:49.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's this late already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:51.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm coming now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:52.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:56.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm confiscating this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:58.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is my book after all, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:03:59.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:05.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Marika-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.55,0:04:07.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she used it as a bookmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:15.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that I think of it, I've never seen\NMarika-chan laugh like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:18.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, Asumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:19.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:22.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:29.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Ringo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:31.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:37.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:41.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I definitely don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:43.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Promise you'll quit if something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:47.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fainting at school is out of the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:49.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:52.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't ever quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm saying this because I'm worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:59.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not taking your medicine, and\Non top of all this, fainting...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:01.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is no way I could let you out in the open.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:06.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:12.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it because you'll be the one in trouble\Nif something happens to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:17.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you have no intention of listening to me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:19.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then I have my own ideas\Non what to do about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:22.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you try to pull strings behind my back,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:24.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll leave this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:29.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd better think of what would\Nhappen if I were to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:32.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that the way you should\Nbe speaking to your father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:37.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The real Marika would never have\Ntaken an attitude like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:41.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop saying it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:44.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you always like that, doing these...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:45.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:52.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the one who keeps\Nsaying the same things!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:57.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why... don't you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:00.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Marika!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:11.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:14.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:15.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:20.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How unusual for you to be rushing in\Nright at the last minute, Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:22.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I was looking for something, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:24.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, Kei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The book I promised to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:28.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:29.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really wanted to read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:33.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone for whom it's even\Nmore unusual just came.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:38.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's usually the first one here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:41.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ladies probably oversleep\Nsometimes, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:45.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Marika-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:45.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:46.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:50.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:02.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was in a book in the storage room at the dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:06.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must have forgotten it\Nwhen you came over last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:11.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a nice photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:12.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see. Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:16.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's taken very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:19.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think Marika-chan's smile is cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:23.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't just look at it as you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:26.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,U-Umm... I'm sorry, Marika-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:28.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I really thought it was a nice photo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:30.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What would you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:34.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quit meddling in my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:41.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:43.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were the ones that saw it without asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi hasn't done anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:55.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Marika-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:02.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:07.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone get changed into your gym\Nclothes and meet in the study room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Was first period Physical Education?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:14.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, maybe there was a change in schedule...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:17.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! We're going to have to run again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:20.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're against running that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:23.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-Not at all... how absurd of you to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:26.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sadly, it isn't a marathon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:28.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can be at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:33.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:40.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:45.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Nakazawa-san who belongs to\Nthe JAMSF Development Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:48.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, please go ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:53.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a one-man capsule\Nfor an emergency escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:58.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In case there is a problem with\Nthe space station or shuttle,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:03.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,this has been created to provide a refuge\Nin space for a short period of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:11.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Within the capsule, there are approximately\N18 hours worth of oxygen,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:16.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and though meager, some food and water.\NAlso, there is an assortment of tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:22.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To take them out, press this area\Nlike this, and the cover will open.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:26.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are there any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:28.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:29.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:32.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a little something that\NI've been wondering about...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:37.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do we get back to the space shuttle\Nafter we escape with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You cannot go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:45.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You will have to wait until help arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:46.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:47.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:47.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That sucks...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:50.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you are placed in a situation\Nwhere you must use this,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:53.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you will need a certain amount of resignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:58.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because there's also the chance that\Nyou could be left behind in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:02.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... I don't even want to think about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:09.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so, you will all go into\Nthe capsule to try it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:16.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It may be tough for those of you who\Nare slightly claustrophobic, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:19.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,this is another part of your training.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:25.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it, a test of endurance, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:28.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The maximum length is 18 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:31.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll end sometime before the\Noxygen runs out, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:33.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmpf, you sure are calm about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:34.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understand, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:39.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be sure you don't come out until the blue\Nlamp inside the capsule turns on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:42.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay... I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:44.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just have to do it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:47.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:50.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, before you go in, put this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:54.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until the training ends,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,absolutely do not drop this
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:58.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or lose this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:10:59.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:01.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:06.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:10.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we lose it, will it really\Nbe that much of a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:12.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lose it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inside this small capsule?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:16.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This might be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:21.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like it's not going to be claustrophobic\Nat all for you, huh, Kamogawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:21.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:28.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now everyone close your hatch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:30.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to engage the lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:40.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you later, Asumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.67,0:11:41.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:54.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Marika-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:02.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's pitch black...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.91,0:12:05.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know what's where with this darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:08.20,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\bord0\frz2.73\pos(164.571,121.715)\blur1\fnSquare721 BT}Status Display Light
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:08.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, it's on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:11.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They said something about\Nthe blue lamp turning on,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:13.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I wonder how long I have to wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:19.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this? Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:21.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're being moved elsewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:25.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:35.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems to have been shaking for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:37.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but is that the kind of\Ntraining it's supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:40.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:42.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shaking stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:45.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel nauseous...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:56.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder how long it's been...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:59.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The blue lamp still hasn't turned on, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:04.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm falling?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:25.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:29.83,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\frz352.1\pos(388.572,117.143)\blur1\c&H5B1E05&}Status Display Light
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blue lamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:31.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's over at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:33.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Release the lock...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:44.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:46.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:13:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:14.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why am I in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:18.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:20.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Marika-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:24.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:26.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:29.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm... all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:33.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could this be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:40.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Survival Training Contents."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:46.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Supposing that during lift-off, or when returning from\Nspace, the rocket has made an emergency landing,"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:50.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"assemble within five days at location A\Nshown on the attached map."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:53.41,Signs,,0,0,0,,{}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:56.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the real training?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:02.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:12.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess they wouldn't make just staying\Nin the capsule the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:15.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, why didn't\Nthey tell us in the first place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:15.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:18.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:31.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're checking our position using the signals\Ncoming out from this device, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:35.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can't call this just training.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:40.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From here on in, everything will probably become\Na criterion for selecting astronauts...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:43.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Promise you'll quit if something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:47.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fainting at school is out of the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:52.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must reach the goal before anyone else!\NI have to reach the goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:21.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no name plate, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:30.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's the use in checking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:34.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I trying to check anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:39.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's left in the capsule is
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:42.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a backpack, sleeping bag, vinyl sheet,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as well as...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:48.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a knife, pen-light, rope, toothpaste...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.33,0:17:51.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So there's no compass...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:54.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It looks as though the food and\Nwater won't even last five days...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:56.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are really only the minimum amount\Nof necessary things in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:01.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to hurry and pinpoint where I am,\Nor I won't be able to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:06.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But with this food situation, it would\Nbe best not to move around so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:08.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll move in the morning tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:11.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And for now, I'd better set up a\Ntent before the sun goes down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:47.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I could see the stars more clearly,\NI'd be able to figure out my bearings...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:54.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if I've just gotten used to life in Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:56.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's so quiet that I can't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:19:00.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder how everyone is doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:07.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I'm like this, it reminds me of the day\NI chased Lion-san deep into the forest...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:11.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That time, it was quiet and\Ncompletely dark just like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:17.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know why, but I couldn't stop my tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:19.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I felt so lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:22.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Scared, sad and all alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:24.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I wanted to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:27.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just really wanted to see him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:20.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}While I was mulling things over,\Nit's already become morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:24.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I spent just one summer with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:27.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I vaguely remembered her face too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:29.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even her name...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:36.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now that I think about it,\Nwhat was her name anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Didn't I ask her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:44.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, even if their faces are alike, their\Nages are just too different, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:46.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's probably just me thinking too much.
