Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:09.79,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\3c&HCAB2AF&\fs20\pos(513.71,354.95)\frz14.91\bord0\b0\fnBottle Shop Faded\c&H5F4F48&}Marika
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:19.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Time to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:27.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All done!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.60,0:21:30.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to brush my teeth after eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.11,0:21:41.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:43.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can do my best until I meet up\Nwith everyone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.18,0:22:15.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was that my imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.89,0:22:19.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought I heard someone's voice...
