Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.32,0:24:37.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One person is my classmate, Marika-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.33,0:24:41.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The other is the Marika-chan that\NLion-san met when he was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.20,0:24:41.20,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\frz14.74\pos(448,237.143)\frx18\fry8\fnHannaHandwriting\blur0.8}Ukita Marika
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.45,0:24:44.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With the times so far apart,\Nwhat's their relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.21,0:24:48.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without knowing what that is,\Nwe wander through the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.09,0:24:53.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But during that time, Marika-chan\Nmeets someone unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.17,0:24:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next time on Twin Spica:\NMarika and Marika.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.01,0:25:00.02,Fireworks,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord0.5\blur2\shad1.5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\pos(430.29,298.43)}Marika and Marika
